{"tid":1147402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無其他聯賽手足已經放棄咗自己嗰隊，準備轉會去英超球隊？","createTime":"2019-05-09T23:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T08:22:44.000Z","uid":134997,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9494fb9129d65b038d22b7aa968a7fc16fc2628f","tid":1147402,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:27:33.000Z","msg":"歷史總係避唔過改朝換代，足球都唔例外，曾幾何時意甲荷甲係頂級聯賽，但係呢家五大聯賽名不副實，只有英超先稱得上係頂級聯賽。<br />\n<br />\n首先講下點解其他四大聯賽開始式微，意甲祖記已經八連冠，德甲拜仁都已經七連冠，西甲方面，之前三連冠嘅皇馬已經連荷甲都比唔上，至於巴塞同馬體呢啲所謂嘅傳統強隊都可以比人反杯，都知道西甲氣數已盡，名存實亡，根本連英乙都不如。<br />\n<br />\n但係英超就唔同，傻仔都知今季歐戰八強四隊入曬，決賽更加係四隊英超包辦，氣勢如虹。有時有啲球迷話西甲勁過英超，真係幼稚，先唔講賽程間歇同體能強度有幾大分別，淨係對手都已經唔同。有大六，有近年冒起嘅狼隊同李城，同埋神秘力量下遊隊。得罪講句，巴馬皇年都只係真正踢兩隊對手，但係英超計埋杯賽，最少有二十隊都要搏盡先贏到，高下立見。<br />\n<br />\n我已經準備好轉去英超球隊，希望近年由英超轉嚟西甲嘅deerhunter可以同我一樣，迷途知返，歡迎英超各路球迷可以入嚟俾下我地呢班迷路小羊意見，等我地投入英超懷抱。"},{"pid":"b74a1b6e733ae7a9bf3f89ff5d630ad3ab686fda","tid":1147402,"uid":232736,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:29:14.000Z","msg":"又打咁長嘅 用咗幾耐時間？"},{"pid":"34e061b97aea9743507024aaec5980d2f3cc8efc","tid":1147402,"uid":134997,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b74a1b6e733ae7a9bf3f89ff5d630ad3ab686fda","tid":1147402,"uid":232736,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:29:14.000Z","msg":"又打咁長嘅 用咗幾耐時間？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:31:25.000Z","msg":"幾個月"},{"pid":"7a186d2bc72b96419458ef3857c094ca5a7f674e","tid":1147402,"uid":9931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:36:18.000Z","msg":"冇睇曬  但撐樓豬的<br />\n<br />\n池中無魚蝦最大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過多排捧你做疤會長"},{"pid":"65a35111efb826fa955f5639cc0eff7ecebffce9","tid":1147402,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a186d2bc72b96419458ef3857c094ca5a7f674e","tid":1147402,"uid":9931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:36:18.000Z","msg":"冇睇曬  但撐樓豬的<br />\n<br />\n池中無魚蝦最大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過多排捧你做疤會長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:37:12.000Z","msg":"撐樓豬就跟我轉會去英超，仲叫我留戀西甲即係推我去死"},{"pid":"2415abdb7f094b646ab06e2c03c12797298c8f5c","tid":1147402,"uid":203961,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:41:22.000Z","msg":"Ching 你已經傷心過度 癲能左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f4a33451f530d020c05f0f04cb81f63525e377","tid":1147402,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34e061b97aea9743507024aaec5980d2f3cc8efc","tid":1147402,"uid":134997,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b74a1b6e733ae7a9bf3f89ff5d630ad3ab686fda","tid":1147402,"uid":232736,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:29:14.000Z","msg":"又打咁長嘅 用咗幾耐時間？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:31:25.000Z","msg":"幾個月"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84e0ad9abc9e0469640cc4e13902fb5e26d3eec","tid":1147402,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2415abdb7f094b646ab06e2c03c12797298c8f5c","tid":1147402,"uid":203961,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:41:22.000Z","msg":"Ching 你已經傷心過度 癲能左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:43:04.000Z","msg":"我地再見亦是朋友，有機會再撐同一隊"},{"pid":"528e0bd268f96595d6a7be4b564cb939da6e7822","tid":1147402,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:45:28.000Z","msg":"疤狗作潮文都要賣隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD吖亨他<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ffa90460206d61910ebeb5ea2a32bdecc49